  * Always initialize PATH (to /bin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/usr/sbin) (closes: #258065)
  * Try harder to remount ro and rw (closes: #259979)
  * Add support for LABEL=/UUID= in checkroot.sh (closes: #261342)

